name: RTCInboundRtpStreamStats.remoteId
description: The remoteId property of the RTCInboundRtpStreamStats dictionary specifies the id of the RTCRemoteOutboundRtpStreamStats object representing the remote peer's RTCRtpSender which is sending the media to the local peer.
